        <item>
            <title>【實試】Fujifilm Instax mini 99 玩光影效果，有玩味的即影即有相機</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/fujifilm-instax-mini-99/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-instax-mini-99</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/fujifilm-instax-mini-99/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 15:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Instax]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Instax mini 99]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[即影即有相機]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1232168</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>不少人用手機影相，po 上 IG 都會加濾鏡。今次這部全新即影即有相機 Fujifilm Instax mini 99 都可以玩類似效果，製造到不同濾鏡效果之餘，竟不用數碼執相，更加原始、更 RAW 更有味道！以下小編就會同 unwire 記者沙律同大家一齊實試。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00190-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00190-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00190.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232197" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00168-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00168-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00168.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232198" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00200-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00200-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00200.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00164-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00164-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00164.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>色彩效果＝物理燈光效果超好玩</h2><p>Fujifilm Instax mini 99 是 mini 90 的升級版本，但就帶來了兩個極之好玩的升級新功能。包括有類似濾鏡的「色彩效果控制」功能，還有模仿懷舊相機的暈影功能。雖然設計簡單，但試過之後實在好玩到停唔到手！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00259-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00259-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00259.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>首先介紹「色彩效果控制」功能。簡單來説就是類似手機 App 的相片濾鏡，但這部相機就完全沒有「數碼味」。打開相機蓋，你可看到鏡頭後方有 4 顆會發光、變色的 LED 燈，在拍攝時發出不同顏色的光芒，直接將色相打入菲林中。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00219-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00219-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00219.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>你可透過相機側邊的轉盤，設定預設定義的顏色組合，包括有 Normal、Fraded Green、Warm Tone、Light Blue、Soft Magenta、Sepia，以及 Light Leak。雖然此功能純粹簡單打燈入菲林，但出來的效果卻令人有驚喜。每張相片都各有風格，適合不同場合使用。即使你跟朋友在同一場地拍照，都可影出不同效果，增添了相片的變化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-1-694x460.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-1-694x460.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00185-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左手邊的轉盤可調節不同的光影效果</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00239-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00239-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00239-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Normal</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00242-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00242-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00242.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Fraded Green</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00243-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00243-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00243.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Warm Tone</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00244-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00244-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00244.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Light Blue</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232181" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00245-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00245-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00245.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Soft Magenta</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00246-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00246-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00246-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Sepia</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232184" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00247-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00247-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00247.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Light Leak</p><h2>物理「暈影」令相片更有 feel</h2><p>Fujifilm Instax mini 99 更加入「暈影模式」，可物理模擬古典相機鏡頭的暈影（黑角）效果。「暈影模式」同樣不是數碼化植入相片，而是靠相機鏡頭前的「VIGNETTE」撥桿。將此撥桿撥向有效時，相機鏡頭面前就會加入一道物理屏障，令你拍出來的相片直接產生黑角。雖然設計簡單，但拍攝出來的效果也是同樣有驚喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232187" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00198-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00198-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00198.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲未開暈影模式，請留意鏡頭中間的鏡片</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00197-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00197-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00197.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在開啟暈影模式後，可看到鏡頭玻璃被一層葉片物理覆蓋，製造成人為的「暈影」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00236-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00236-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00236.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232186" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00235-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00235-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00235.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>除了上面兩個新玩法，Instax mini 99 備有 5 個等級的光度調節。好多人認為 Instax 的相片不夠光，現在你就可自由調校曝光度。從 D-, D, -, L, L+ 共 5 級光度水平。簡單來説相片愈光就愈低反差、低對比，讓你在日光拍攝時增添日系風味。而較黑的相片則會看上去較高對比，有另一番風味。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232189" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00165-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00165-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00165.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Instax mini 99 與上代 mini 90 一樣設有風景、微距模式。在相機鏡頭的轉盤上，你可調校 0.3~0.6m、0.6m~3m，以及 3m~ 無限遠，適合不同拍攝情景。在拍攝小物時，利用 0.3~0.6m 模式，就可做到了一點淺景深效果。另外相機自拍功能、雙重曝光模式都在 mini 99 上用到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00228-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00228-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00228.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00183-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00183-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00183.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次 mini 99 採用可拆卸式電池，並隨產品附有充電機，讓你隨時充電。產品更有一個可插在三腳架螺紋的手柄，讓你在自拍時更加輕鬆。</p><p>Instax mini 99 發售日期：2024 年 4 月 25 日</p><p>建議零售價：HK$1,580</p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232199" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00204-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00204-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc00204.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/28/fujifilm-gfx100s-xt50-mirrorless-camera-may-16/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">網絡爆料 Fujifilm GFX100S II   聯同 X-T50 無反相機 5 月中發表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/29/fujifilm-limited-edition-camera/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">慶祝品牌成立 90 週年，限量版 Fujifilm X100VI 中國消費者有額外著數</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/06/fujifilm-x100vi-unveil-no-d-pad/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Fujifilm X100VI 外觀流出　新機疑剔除 D-Pad</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/fujifilm-instax-mini-99/dc/">【實試】Fujifilm Instax mini 99 玩光影效果，有玩味的即影即有相機</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
